move1.name: Tackle
move1.description: A physical attack in which the user charges and slams into the target with its whole body.

move2.name: Vine Whip
move2.description: The target is struck with slender, whiplike vines to inflict damage.

move3.name: Razor Leaf
move3.description: Sharp-edged leaves are launched to slash at opposing Pokémon. Critical hits land more easily.

move4.name: Solar Beam
move4.description: In this two-turn attack, the user gathers energy and blasts a bundled beam on the next turn.

move1.name: Peck
move1.description: The target is jabbed with a sharply pointed beak or horn.

move2.name: Drill Peck
move2.description: A corkscrewing attack that strikes the target with a sharp beak acting as a drill.

move3.name: Gust
move3.description: A gust of wind is whipped up by wings and launched at the target to inflict damage.

move4.name: Aerial Ace
move4.description: The user confounds the target with a swift and cutting air current. This attack always strikes first and cannot be evaded.

move1.name: Absorb
move1.description: A nutrient-draining attack. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.

move2.name: Acid
move2.description: The opposing Pokémon are attacked with a spray of harsh acid. This may also lower their Sp. Def stat.

move3.name: Petal Dance
move3.description: The user attacks the target by scattering petals for two to three turns. The user then becomes confused.

move4.name: Sludge Bomb
move4.description: The user strikes the target with a sludge bomb. It may also poison the target.

move1.name: Slash
move1.description: The target is attacked with a slash of claws or blades. Critical hits land more easily.

move2.name: Earth Power
move2.description: The user makes the ground under the target erupt with power. It may also lower the target's Sp. Def.

move3.name: Earthquake
move3.description: The user sets off an earthquake that strikes every Pokémon around it.

move4.name: Stone Edge
move4.description: The user stabs the target from below with sharpened stones. Critical hits land more easily.

move1.name: Scratch
move1.description: Hard, pointed, sharp claws rake the target to inflict damage.

move2.name: Water Gun
move2.description: The target is blasted with a forceful shot of water.

move3.name: Confusion
move3.description: The target is struck by a peculiar ray. This may also leave the target confused.

move4.name: Hydro Pump
move4.description: The target is blasted with a giant volume of water launched under great pressure.

move1.name: Bite
move1.description: The target is bitten with viciously sharp fangs. It may make the target flinch.

move2.name: Flamethrower
move2.description: The target is scorched with an intense blast of fire. It may also leave the target with a burn.

move3.name: Extreme Speed
move3.description: The user charges at the target with blinding speed. This move always goes first.

move4.name: Fire Blast
move4.description: The target is attacked with an intense blast of all-consuming fire. It may also leave the target with a burn.

move1.name: Psybeam
move1.description: The target is attacked with a peculiar ray. It may also confuse the target.

move2.name: Confusion
move2.description: The target is struck by a peculiar ray. This may also leave the target confused.

move3.name: Shadow Ball
move3.description: The user hurls a shadowy blob at the target. It may also lower the target's Special Defense stat.

move4.name: Psychic
move4.description: The target is hit by a strong telekinetic force. It may also reduce the target's Special Defense stat.

move1.name: Karate Chop
move1.description: The target is attacked with a sharp chop. Critical hits land more easily.

move2.name: Low Sweep
move2.description: The user makes a swift attack on the target's legs, which lowers the target's Speed stat.

move3.name: Cross Chop
move3.description: The user delivers a double chop with its forearms crossed. Critical hits land more easily.

move4.name: Submission
move4.description: The user grabs the target and recklessly dives for the ground. It also hurts the user slightly.

move2.name: Sludge Bomb

move3.name: Seed Bomb

move4.name: Power Whip
move4.description: The user violently whips its vines or tentacles to strike the target. This may also make the target flinch.

move1.name: Rock Throw

move2.name: Magnitude

move1.name: Drill Peck

move3.name: Aurora Beam
